This document describes the architecture
of the maison platform in a visual way
with all the components and how they
interact with each other. \

g.title: Cert-Manager is a Kubernetes controller that automates the management and issuance of TLS certificates.
ExternalDNS is a Kubernetes controller that configures DNS resources.
TailScale is a mesh VPN that makes it easy to connect your devices, wherever they are.
Open and extensible continuous delivery solution for Kubernetes
Traefik is a modern HTTP reverse proxy and load balancer.
External-Secret is a Kubernetes controller that allows you to use external secret management systems.
CloudNativePG is a comprehensive platform designed to seamlessly manage PostgreSQL databases within Kubernetes environments.
FileFlows is a file processing application that can execute actions against a file in a tree flow structure.
Jellyfin is the volunteer-built media solution that puts you in control of your media.
Free and open source software application for managing requests for Jellyfin libraries.
Actual Budget is a personal finance app that helps you track your spending and save money.
Intuitive and easy to use recipe management app.
Paperless-ngx is a community-supported open-source document management system that transforms your physical documents into a searchable online archive.
Secure and AI-native workflow automation tool for technical people.
A modern, open source low-code platform for building modern internal applications in minutes.
Linkding is a self-hosted bookmarking and link aggregation service.
